of Aggression','C15','Instant','U','{3}{PR}{PR}','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'#_({PR} can be paid with either {R} or 2 life.)_#£Gain control of target creature an opponent controls until end of turn. Untap that creature. It gains haste until end of turn.',NULL,NULL,'Whit Brachna','141','5','£6/1/2011: A card with Phyrexian mana symbols in its mana cost is each color that appears in that mana cost, regardless of how that cost may have been paid.£6/1/2011: To calculate the converted mana cost of a card with Phyrexian mana symbols in its cost, count each Phyrexian mana symbol as 1.£6/1/2011: As you cast a spell or activate an activated ability with one or more Phyrexian mana symbols in its cost, you choose how to pay for each Phyrexian mana symbol at the same time you would choose modes or choose a value for X.£6/1/2011: If you’re at 1 life or less, you can’t pay 2 life.£6/1/2011: Phyrexian mana is not a new color. Players can’t add Phyrexian mana to their mana pools.£6/1/2011: Act of Aggression can target any creature an opponent controls, even one that’s untapped.£6/1/2011: Gaining control of a creature doesn’t cause you to gain control of any Auras or Equipment attached to it.','R',NULL,'0.06','0.23','1.66',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'R','侵略行为',NULL,'Acte d''agressivité','Aggressionsakt','Atto d''Aggressione','攻撃的な行動',NULL,NULL,'Acto de agresión',NULL,'瞬间',NULL,'Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo','インスタント',NULL,NULL,'Instantáneo',NULL,'（{PR}可用{R}或2点生命来支付。）获得目标由对手操控的生物之操控权直到回合结束。重置该生物。它获得敏捷异能直到回合结束。',NULL,'#_({PR} peut être payé au choix avec {R} ou 2 points de vie.)_# Acquérez le contrôle d''une créature ciblée qu''un adversaire contrôle jusqu''à la fin du tour. Dégagez cette créature. Elle acquiert la célérité jusqu''à la fin du tour.','#_({PR} kann entweder mit {R} oder 2 Lebenspunkten bezahlt werden.)_# Übernimm bis zum Ende des Zuges die Kontrolle über eine Kreatur deiner Wahl, die ein Gegner kontrolliert. Enttappe diese Kreatur. Sie erhält Eile bis zum Ende des Zuges.','#_({PR} può essere pagato con {R} o con 2 punti vita.)_# Prendi il controllo di una creatura bersaglio controllata da un avversario fino alla fine del turno. STAPpa quella creatura. Ha rapidità fino alla fine del turno.','（{PR}は{R}でも２点のライフでも支払うことができる。）対戦相手がコントロールするクリーチャー１体を対象とし、ターン終了時まで、それのコントロールを得る。そのクリーチャーをアンタップする。ターン終了時まで、それは速攻を得る。',NULL,NULL,'#_({PR} puede pagarse con {R} o con 2 vidas.)_# Gana el control de la criatura objetivo que controla un oponente hasta el final del turno. Endereza esa criatura. Gana la habilidad de prisa hasta el final del turno.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405119','Aetherize','C15','Instant','U','{3}{U}','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Return all attacking creatures to their owner''s hand.','#_"You can come back once you''ve learned some manners—and figured out how to reconstitute your physical forms."_#',NULL,'Ryan Barger','85','5','£11/17/2017: An “attacking creature” is one that has been declared as an attacker this combat, or one that was put onto the battlefield attacking this combat. Unless that creature leaves combat, it continues to be an attacking creature through the end of combat step, even if the player it was attacking has left the game, or the planeswalker it was attacking has left combat. There’s no such thing as an attacking creature outside of the combat phase.','U',NULL,'N/A','N/A','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'U',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'瞬间',NULL,'Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo','インスタント',NULL,NULL,'Instantáneo',NULL,'将所有进行攻击的生物移回其拥有者手上。',NULL,'Renvoyez toutes les créatures attaquantes dans la main de leur propriétaire.','Bringe alle angreifenden Kreaturen auf die Hand ihrer Besitzer zurück.','Fai tornare tutte le creature attaccanti in mano ai rispettivi proprietari.','すべての攻撃クリーチャーをオーナーの手札に戻す。',NULL,NULL,'Regresa todas las criaturas atacantes a las manos de sus propietarios.',NULL,'#_「等你学会礼貌，想出如何重构你的形体后就可以回来。」_#',NULL,'#_« Revenez quand vous aurez appris les bonnes manières... et trouvé le moyen de reconstituer vos corps. »_#','#_„Du kannst zurückkommen, sobald du Manieren hast und weißt, wie du deine körperliche Gestalt wiederherstellen kannst."_#','#_"Torna quando avrai imparato le buone maniere… e a ricostituire la tua forma fisica."_#','#_「少し礼儀というものを学んでから出直すんだな――それに、肉体を再構成する方法も見つけたほうがいい。」_#',NULL,NULL,'#_"Vuelve cuando aprendas modales... y hayas averiguado cómo reconstruir tu estructura física"._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405120','Aethersnatch','C15','Instant','R','{4}{U}{U}','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Gain control of target spell. You may choose new targets for it. #_(If that spell becomes a permanent, it enters the battlefield under your control.)_#','#_"You were saying?"_#',NULL,'Aaron Miller','9','5','£11/4/2015: Aethersnatch can target any spell, even one without targets.£11/4/2015: If you gain control of an instant or sorcery spell, it will be put into its owner’s graveyard as it resolves.£11/4/2015: You may change any or none of the spell’s targets. If you change a target, you must choose a legal target for the spell. If you can’t, you must leave the target unchanged (even if the current target is illegal). Notably, if you were originally chosen as a “target opponent” for a spell you gain control with Aethersnatch, you are now an illegal target as you aren’t your own opponent.£11/4/2015: Combat damage dealt by a commander is tracked without regard to who controlled the commander at the time it dealt damage. For example, say a commander deals 10 combat damage to a player, leaves the battlefield, is recast, and you gain control of it with Aethersnatch. If it deals another 11 combat damage to that same player, they will lose the game.£11/4/2015: If you gain control of a commander spell, the commander’s owner chooses whether to put it in the command zone if it later leaves the battlefield.','U',NULL,'N/A','N/A','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'U',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'瞬间',NULL,'Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo','インスタント',NULL,NULL,'Instantáneo',NULL,'获得目标咒语的操控权。你可以为它选择新的目标。（如果该咒语成为永久物，则它会在你的操控下进战场。）',NULL,'Acquérez le contrôle du sort ciblé. Vous pouvez choisir de nouvelles cibles pour celui-ci. #_(Si ce sort devient un permanent, il arrive sur le champ de bataille sous votre contrôle.)_#','Übernimm die Kontrolle über einen Zauberspruch deiner Wahl. Du kannst neue Ziele für ihn bestimmen. #_(Falls der Zauberspruch zu einer bleibenden Karte wird, kommt sie unter deiner Kontrolle ins Spiel.)_#','Prendi il controllo di una magia bersaglio. Puoi scegliere nuovi bersagli per essa. #_(Se quella magia diventa un permanente, entra nel campo di battaglia sotto il tuo controllo.)_#','呪文１つを対象とし、それのコントロールを得る。あなたはそれの新しい対象を選んでもよい。（その呪文がパーマネントとなるなら、それはあなたのコントロール下で戦場に出る。）',NULL,NULL,'Gana el control del hechizo objetivo. Puedes elegir nuevos objetivos para él. #_(Si ese hechizo se convierte en un permanente, entra al campo de batalla bajo tu control.)_#',NULL,'#_「你说什么来着？」_#',NULL,'#_« Vous disiez ? »_#','#_„Wolltest du gerade etwas sagen?"_#','#_"Dicevi, scusa?"_#','#_「何を言おうとしてたの？」_#',NULL,NULL,'#_"¿Decías algo?"._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405121','Ajani''s Chosen','C15','Creature — Cat Soldier','R','{2}{W}{W}','4','3','3',NULL,'Whenever an enchantment enters the battlefield under your control, create a 2/2 white Cat creature token. If that enchantment is an Aura, you may attach it to the token.','#_"United, our roar will level mountains."_#',NULL,'Wayne Reynolds','57','5','£7/1/2013: The ability doesn’t trigger until the enchantment enters the battlefield. This means that, for example, you can’t cast an Aura with enchant creature if there are no legal targets available, hoping to enchant the Cat token. Ajani’s Chosen itself, however, may be a legal target for the Aura.£7/1/2013: If you cast an Aura targeting an opponent or a permanent controlled by an opponent, you control that Aura when it enters the battlefield. The ability of Ajani’s Chosen will trigger.£7/1/2013: You may attach the Aura to the token only if it can legally enchant that token. For example, if the enchantment that entered the battlefield is an Aura with “enchant land,” it won’t move.£7/1/2013: You may attach the Aura to the Cat token only if the Aura and the token are both on the battlefield when the triggered ability resolves. If the Aura leaves the battlefield before the ability resolves, it won’t become attached to the token. If the token leaves the battlefield before the ability resolves, the Aura won’t move.','W',NULL,'0.19','0.41','1.2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W','阿耶尼的精卫',NULL,'Élus d''Ajani','Ajanis Auserwählte','Prescelti di Ajani','アジャニに選ばれし者',NULL,NULL,'Elegido de Ajani',NULL,'生物～猫／士兵',NULL,'Créature : chat et soldat','Kreatur — Katze, Soldat','Creatura — Soldato Felino','クリーチャー ― 猫・兵士',NULL,NULL,'Criatura — Soldado felino',NULL,'每当一个结界在你的操控下进战场时，将一个2/2白色的猫衍生生物放进战场。若该结界是灵气，你可以将它结附在该衍生物上。',NULL,'À chaque fois qu''un enchantement arrive sur le champ de bataille sous votre contrôle, mettez sur le champ de bataille un jeton de créature 2/2 blanche Chat. Si cet enchantement est une aura, vous pouvez l''attacher au jeton.','Immer wenn eine Verzauberung unter deiner Kontrolle ins Spiel kommt, bringe einen 2/2 weißen Katze-Kreaturenspielstein ins Spiel. Falls diese Verzauberung eine Aura ist, kannst du sie an den Spielstein anlegen.','Ogniqualvolta un incantesimo entra nel campo di battaglia sotto il tuo controllo, metti sul campo di battaglia una pedina creatura Felino 2/2 bianca. Se quell''incantesimo è un''Aura, puoi assegnarla alla pedina.','エンチャントが１つあなたのコントロール下で戦場に出るたび、白の２/２の猫・クリーチャー・トークンを１体戦場に出す。そのエンチャントがオーラであるなら、あなたはそれをそのトークンにつけてもよい。',NULL,NULL,'Siempre que un encantamiento entre al campo de batalla bajo tu control, pon en el campo de batalla una ficha de criatura Felino blanca 2/2. Si ese encantamiento es un aura, puedes anexarlo a la ficha.',NULL,'#_「团结起来，我们的吼声将夷平高山。」_#',NULL,'#_« Ensemble, notre rugissement pulvérisera les montagnes. »_#','#_„Vereint wird unser Gebrüll ganze Berge einebnen."_#','#_"Insieme, il nostro ruggito spianerà le montagne."_#','#_「団結すれば、我らが咆哮は山をも更地にするだろう。」_#',NULL,NULL,'#_"Unidos, nuestro rugido arrasará montañas"._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405122','Altar''s Reap','C15','Instant','C','{1}{B}','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'As an additional cost to cast this spell, sacrifice a creature.£Draw two cards.','#_"Don''t worry, your death will be as informative as possible."—Gorghul, augur of skulls_#',NULL,'Donato Giancola','112','5','£4/15/2013: You must sacrifice exactly one creature to cast this spell; you cannot cast it without sacrificing a creature, and you cannot sacrifice additional creatures.£4/15/2013: Players can only respond once this spell has been cast and all its costs have been paid. No one can try to destroy the creature you sacrificed to prevent you from casting this spell.','B',NULL,'0.05','0.15','0.95',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B','祭坛夺命',NULL,'Fenaison de l''autel','Ernte des Altars','Raccolto dell''Altare','祭壇の刈り取り',NULL,NULL,'Cosecha del altar',NULL,'瞬间',NULL,'Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo','インスタント',NULL,NULL,'Instantáneo',NULL,'牺牲一个生物，以作为施放祭坛夺命的额外费用。抓两张牌。',NULL,'En tant que coût supplémentaire pour lancer la Fenaison de l''autel, sacrifiez une créature.Piochez deux cartes.','Opfere eine Kreatur als zusätzliche Kosten, um die Ernte des Altars zu wirken.Ziehe zwei Karten.','Come costo addizionale per lanciare il Raccolto dell''Altare, sacrifica una creatura.Pesca due carte.','祭壇の刈り取りを唱えるための追加コストとして、クリーチャーを１体生け贄に捧げる。カードを２枚引く。',NULL,NULL,'Como coste adicional para lanzar la Cosecha del altar, sacrifica una criatura.Roba dos cartas.',NULL,'#_「别担心，我们会尽力从你的死亡取得大量情报。」～颅骨卜算师苟古_#',NULL,'#_« N''aie crainte, ta mort sera particulièrement informative. »—Gorghul, augure des crânes_#','#_„Keine Sorge, dein Tod wird so informativ wie möglich sein."—Gorghul, Schädel-Augur_#','#_"Non preoccuparti, la tua morte ci fornirà moltissime informazioni utili."—Gorghul, augure dei teschi_#','#_「大丈夫、お前の死からなるべく多く学べるようにするからな。」――髑髏の占い師、ゴーガル_#',NULL,NULL,'#_"No te preocupes: haré tu muerte tan educativa como me sea posible".—Górghul, presagio de cráneos_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405123','Ambition''s Cost','C15','Sorcery','U','{3}{B}','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'You draw three cards and you lose 3 life.','#_The waters of wisdom are as dust in the mouth of one who thirsts for power._#',NULL,'Junko Taguchi','113','5',NULL,'B',NULL,'0.05','0.26','0.95',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B','野心的代价',NULL,'Le prix de l''ambition','Preis des Ehrgeizes','Costo dell''Ambizione','野望の代償',NULL,NULL,'El precio de la ambición',NULL,'法术',NULL,'Rituel','Hexerei','Stregoneria','ソーサリー',NULL,NULL,'Conjuro',NULL,'你抓三张牌且失去3点生命。',NULL,'Vous piochez trois cartes et vous perdez 3 points de vie.','Du ziehst drei Karten und verlierst 3 Lebenspunkte.','Pesca tre carte e perdi 3 punti vita.','あなたはカードを３枚引き、３点のライフを失う。',NULL,NULL,'Robas tres cartas y pierdes 3 vidas.',NULL,'#_对渴求权力者而言，知识之水干涩如尘。_#',NULL,'#_Un océan de sagesse n''est que poussière pour quiconque a soif de pouvoir._#','#_Die Wasser des Wissens werden zu Staub im Munde derer, die nach Macht dürsten._#','#_Le acque della saggezza sono come polvere nella bocca di chi è assetato di potere._#','#_英知の水は、権力を渇望する者が口にしても粉塵にしかならない。_#',NULL,NULL,'#_Las aguas del conocimiento son igual que polvo en la garganta de quien tiene sed de poder._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405124','Ancient Amphitheater','C15','Land','R',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'As Ancient Amphitheater enters the battlefield, you may reveal a Giant card from your hand. If you don''t, Ancient Amphitheater enters the battlefield tapped.£{T}: Add {R} or {W}.','#_The arbiter Galanda Feudkiller judges Lorwyn''s squabbles from a lofty perspective._#',NUL