ing','C15','Sorcery','R','{3}{B}','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'You draw three cards and you lose 3 life.','#_Knowledge demands sacrifice._#',NULL,'Rob Alexander','114','5',NULL,'B',NULL,'0.13','0.39','1.2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B','远古渴望',NULL,'Passion pour l''antique','Uraltes Verlangen','Desiderio Atavico','古えの渇望',NULL,NULL,'Anhelo antiguo',NULL,'法术',NULL,'Rituel','Hexerei','Stregoneria','ソーサリー',NULL,NULL,'Conjuro',NULL,'你抓三张牌且失去3点生命。',NULL,'Vous piochez trois cartes et vous perdez 3 points de vie.','Du ziehst drei Karten und verlierst 3 Lebenspunkte.','Pesca tre carte e perdi 3 punti vita.','あなたはカードを３枚引き、３点のライフを失う。',NULL,NULL,'Robas tres cartas y pierdes 3 vidas.',NULL,'#_要牺牲才能获取知识。_#',NULL,'#_Le savoir exige un sacrifice._#','#_Wissen verlangt Opfer._#','#_La conoscenza richiede sacrifici._#','#_知識は犠牲を求める。_#',NULL,NULL,'#_El conocimiento exige sacrificio._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405126','Angel of Serenity','C15','Creature — Angel','M','{4}{W}{W}{W}','7','5','6',NULL,'Flying£When Angel of Serenity enters the battlefield, you may exile up to three other target creatures from the battlefield and/or creature cards from graveyards.£When Angel of Serenity leaves the battlefield, return the exiled cards to their owners'' hands.',NULL,NULL,'Aleksi Briclot','58','5','£10/1/2012: If Angel of Serenity leaves the battlefield before its enters-the-battlefield ability has resolved, its leaves-the-battlefield ability will trigger and do nothing. Then the enters-the-battlefield ability will resolve and exile the targeted creatures and/or creature cards indefinitely.£1/24/2013: You choose up to three total targets from among other creatures on the battlefield and creature cards in graveyards. You may choose zero targets.£1/24/2013: You choose the targets as part of putting the enters-the-battlefield trigger on the stack. Because that ability includes “you may,” you choose whether to exile the targets when the ability resolves.£1/24/2013: If a