 del turno.','対戦相手１人を対象とする。あなたがコントロールするすべてのクリーチャーと、そのプレイヤーがコントロールするすべてのクリーチャーをアンタップする。ターン終了時まで、あなたとそのプレイヤーはそれぞれ、もう一方がコントロールするすべてのクリーチャーのコントロールを得る。ターン終了時まで、それらのクリーチャーは速攻を得る。',NULL,NULL,'Endereza todas las criaturas que controlas y todas las criaturas que controla el oponente objetivo. Tanto tú como ese oponente ganan el control de todas las criaturas que controla el otro hasta el final del turno. Esas criaturas ganan la habilidad de prisa hasta el final del turno.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405356','Reliquary Tower','C15','Land','U',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'You have no maximum hand size.£{T}: Add {C}.','#_Once guarded by the Knights of the Reliquary, the tower stands now protected only by its own remoteness, its dusty treasures open to plunder by anyone._#',NULL,'Jesper Ejsing','301','5','£2/1/2009: If multiple effects modify your hand size, apply them in timestamp order. For example, if you put Null Profusion (an enchantment that says your maximum hand size is two) onto the battlefield and then put Reliquary Tower onto the battlefield, you’ll have no maximum hand size. However, if those permanents enter the battlefield in the opposite order, your maximum hand size would be two.','L','{C}','3.45','5.7','9.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'圣物塔',NULL,'Tour du Reliquaire','Turm des Reliquienschreins','Torre del Reliquiario','聖遺の塔',NULL,NULL,'Torre del relicario',NULL,'地',NULL,'Terrain','Land','Terra','土地',NULL,NULL,'Tierra',NULL,'你的手牌数量没有上限。{T}：加{1}到你的法术力池中。',NULL,'Il n''y a pas de limite au nombre de cartes dans votre main.{T} : Ajoutez {1} à votre réserve.','Es gibt keine Obergrenze für die Anzahl an Karten, die du auf der Hand halten darfst.{T}: Erhöhe deinen Manavorrat um {1}.','Non hai un limite massimo di carte nella tua mano.{T}: Aggiungi {1} alla tua riserva di mana.','あなたの手札の上限はなくなる。{T}：あなたのマナ・プールに{1}を加える。',NULL,NULL,'Tu mano no tiene tamaño máximo.{T}: Agrega {1} a tu reserva de maná.',NULL,'#_圣物塔从前由圣物骑士守护，但如今保护它的只剩它与人世的疏离，任谁都可轻易掠尽它那积满尘土的珍宝。_#',NULL,'#_Autrefois gardée par les Chevaliers du Reliquaire, la tour n''est plus protégée que par son isolement et ses trésors poussiéreux sont à la merci du premier pillard._#','#_Der einst von den Rittern des Reliquienschreins bewachte Turm wird nun nur durch seine entfernte Lage geschützt. Seine staubigen Schätze stehen jedem Plünderer offen._#','#_Un tempo difesa dai Cavalieri del Reliquiario, la torre è adesso protetta unicamente dalla propria inaccessibilità; chiunque potrà saccheggiarne i polverosi tesori._#','#_昔、聖遺の騎士によって守られていたその塔は、外界から隔絶しているおかげで今でも立ち続けている。誰でも埃をかぶった宝物の数々を我が物にできるのだ。_#',NULL,NULL,'#_Custodiada en otros tiempos por los Caballeros del Relicario, la torre se alza ahora protegida sólo por su propia lejanía y con sus polvorientos tesoros expuestos a cualquier saqueador._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405357','Repeal','C15','Instant','C','{X}{U}','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Return target nonland permanent with converted mana cost X to its owner''s hand.£Draw a card.','#_"Your deed cannot be undone. You, however, can be."—Agosto, Azorius imperator_#',NULL,'Anthony Palumbo','104','5',NULL,'U',NULL,'0.05','0.18','0.95',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'U','撤回',NULL,'Abrogation','Aufhebung','Abrogare','撤廃',NULL,NULL,'Revocar',NULL,'瞬间',NULL,'Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo','インスタント',NULL,NULL,'Instantáneo',NULL,'将目标总法术力费用为X的非地永久物移回其拥有者手上。抓一张牌。',NULL,'Renvoyez le permanent non-terrain ciblé ayant un coût converti de mana de X dans la main de son propriétaire.Piochez une carte.','Bringe eine bleibende Karte deiner Wahl, die kein Land ist und deren umgewandelte Manakosten X betragen, auf die Hand ihres Besitzers zurück.Ziehe eine Karte.','Fai tornare un permanente non terra bersaglio con costo di mana convertito pari a X in mano al suo proprietario.Pesca una carta.','点数で見たマナ・コストがＸの土地でないパーマネント１つを対象とし、それをオーナーの手札に戻す。カードを１枚引く。',NULL,NULL,'Regresa el permanente objetivo que no sea tierra con coste de maná convertido de X a la mano de su propietario.Roba una carta.',NULL,'#_「你的约定不能毁弃。但你，倒是可以。」～俄佐立将军阿果托_#',NULL,'#_« Ce qui est fait est fait. Ce qui existe peut être annulé. »—Agosto, imperator d''Azorius_#','#_„Dein Verbrechen kann nicht wieder rückgängig gemacht werden. Du hingegen schon."—Agosto, Imperator der Azorius_#','#_"Ciò che hai fatto non può più essere disfatto. Tu, invece, sì."—Agosto, imperatore Azorius_#','#_「お前の行いは無かったことにはできぬ。しかし、お前をそうすることは可能だ。」――アゾリウスの将軍、アゴスト_#',NULL,NULL,'#_"Tu acción no puede ser deshecha. Sin embargo, tu sí puedes serlo".—Agosto, imperator azorio_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405358','Righteous Confluence','C15','Sorcery','R','{3}{W}{W}','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Choose three. You may choose the same mode more than once.£• Create a 2/2 white Knight creature token with vigilance.£• Exile target enchantment.£• You gain 5 life.',NULL,NULL,'Kieran Yanner','7','5','£11/4/2015: If the third mode is chosen multiple times, each of those modes represents a separate life-gaining event. For example, if the third mode is chosen three times, and you control Karlov of the Ghost Council (a creature with the ability “Whenever you gain life, put two +1/+1 counters on Karlov of the Ghost Council.”), Karlov’s ability will trigger three times, for a total of six +1/+1 counters.£11/4/2015: You choose the modes as you cast the spell. Once modes are chosen, they can’t be changed.£11/4/2015: If a mode requires a target, you can select that mode only if there’s a legal target available. Ignore the targeting requirements for modes you don’t choose. Each time you select that mode, you can choose a different target, or you can choose the same target.£11/4/2015: No matter which combination of modes you choose, you always follow the instructions of a Confluence in the order they are written. If the same mode is chosen more than once, you choose their relative order as you cast the spell.£11/4/2015: No player can cast spells or activate abilities in between the modes of a resolving spell.£11/4/2015: If a Confluence is copied, the effect that creates the copy will usually allow you to choose new targets, but you can’t choose new modes.£11/4/2015: If all targets for the chosen modes become illegal before the Confluence resolves, the spell won’t resolve and none of its effects will happen. If at least one target is still legal, the spell will resolve but will have no effect on any illegal targets.','W',NULL,'0.25','0.71','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W','正气交汇',NULL,'Confluence vertueuse','Rechtschaffene Konfluenz','Confluenza Virtuosa','正義の合流点',NULL,NULL,'Confluencia justa',NULL,'法术',NULL,'Rituel','Hexerei','Stregoneria','ソーサリー',NULL,NULL,'Conjuro',NULL,'选择三项。你可以多次选择同一项。• 将一个2/2白色，具警戒异能的骑士衍生生物放进战场。• 放逐目标结界。• 你获得5点生命。',NULL,'Choisissez trois. Vous pouvez choisir le même mode plus d''une fois.• Mettez sur le champ de bataille un jeton de créature 2/2 blanche Chevalier avec la vigilance.• Exilez l''enchantement ciblé.• Vous gagnez 5 points de vie.','Bestimme drei. Du kannst denselben Modus mehr als einmal bestimmen.• Bringe einen 2/2 weißen Ritter-Kreaturenspielstein mit Wachsamkeit ins Spiel.• Schicke eine Verzauberung deiner Wahl ins Exil.• Du erhältst 5 Lebenspunkte dazu.','Scegli tre. Puoi scegliere lo stesso modo più di una volta.• Metti sul campo di battaglia una pedina creatura Cavaliere 2/2 bianca con cautela.• Esilia un incantesimo bersaglio.• Guadagni 5 punti vita.','以下から３つを選ぶ。同じモードを２回以上選んでもよい。• 警戒を持つ白の２/２の騎士・クリーチャー・トークンを１体戦場に出す。• エンチャント１つを対象とし、それを追放する。• あなたは５点のライフを得る。',NULL,NULL,'Elige tres. Puedes elegir el mismo modo más de una vez.• Pon en el campo de batalla una ficha de criatura Caballero blanca 2/2 con la habilidad de vigilancia.• Exilia el encantamiento objetivo.• Ganas 5 vidas.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405359','Rise from the Grave','C15','Sorcery','U','{4}{B}','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Put target creature card from a graveyard onto the battlefield under your control. That creature is a black Zombie in addition to its other colors and types.','#_"Death is no excuse for disobedience."—Liliana Vess_#',NULL,'Vance Kovacs','134','5','£10/1/2009: Rise from the Grave doesn’t overwrite any previous colors or types. Rather, it adds another color and another subtype.£10/1/2009: If the targeted creature is normally colorless, it will simply become black. It won’t be both black and colorless.£10/1/2009: A later effect that changes the affected creature’s colors will overwrite that part of Rise from the Grave effect; the creature will be just the new color. The same is true about an effect that changes the affected creature’s types or subtypes.£10/1/2009: A “creature card” is any card with the type creature, even if it has other types such as artifact, enchantment, or land. Older cards of type summon are also creature cards.','B',NULL,'0.03','0.21','1.2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B','坟场复生',NULL,'Reviviscence','Von den Toten auferstehen','Risuscitare','墓場からの復活',NULL,NULL,'Levantarse de la tumba',NULL,'法术',NULL,'Rituel','Hexerei','Stregoneria','ソーサリー',NULL,NULL,'Conjuro',NULL,'将目标生物牌在你的操控下从坟墓场放进战场。该生物额外具有黑色此颜色与灵俑此类别。',NULL,'Mettez sur le champ de bataille, sous votre contrôle, une carte de créature ciblée depuis un cimetière. Cette créature est un zombie noir en plus de ses autres couleurs et de ses autres types.','Bringe eine Kreaturenkarte deiner Wahl aus einem Friedhof unter deiner Kontrolle ins Spiel. Diese Kreatur ist zusätzlich zu ihren anderen Farben und Typen ein schwarzer Zombie.','Metti sul campo di battaglia sotto il tuo controllo una carta creatura bersaglio da un cimitero. Quella creatura è uno Zombie nero in aggiunta ai suoi altri tipi e colori.','墓地にあるクリーチャー・カード１枚を対象とし、それをあなたのコントロール下で戦場に出す。そのクリーチャーは、他の色やタイプに加えて黒のゾンビでもある。',NULL,NULL,'Pon en el campo de batalla bajo tu control la carta de criatura objetivo de un cementerio. Esa criatura es un Zombie negro además de sus otros colores y tipos.',NULL,'#_「死亡不是抗命的藉口。」～莉莲娜维斯_#',NULL,'#_« La mort n''excuse pas la désobéissance. »—Liliana Vess_#','#_„Tod ist kein Grund für Ungehorsam."—Liliana Vess_#','#_"La morte non è una scusa per disobbedire."—Liliana Vess_#','#_「死んでるから従わなくていいってことはないね。」――リリアナ・ヴェス_#',NULL,NULL,'#_"La muerte no es una excusa para desobedecer".—Liliana Vess_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405360','Rite of Replication','C15','Sorcery','R','{2}{U}{U}','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Kicker {5} #_(You may pay an additional {5} as you cast this spell.)_#£Create a token that''s a copy of target creature. If this spell was kicked, create five of those tokens instead.',NULL,NULL,'Matt Cavotta','105','5','£10/1/2009: If the targeted creature is an illegal target by the time Rite of Replication resolves, the entire spell doesn’t resolve. You won’t get any tokens.£10/1/2009: As the token or tokens are created, they check the printed values of the creature they’re copying — or, if that creature is itself a token, the original characteristics of that token as stated by the effect that put it onto the battlefield — as well as any copy effects that have been applied to it. It won’t copy counters on the creature, nor will it copy other effects that have changed the creature’s power, toughness, types, color, or so on.£10/1/2009: The tokens see each other enter the battlefield. If they have a triggered ability that triggers when a creature enters the battlefield, they’ll all trigger for one another.','U',NULL,'3.5','4.47','7.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'U','模造仪式',NULL,'Rite de duplication','Replikationsritual','Rito di Riproduzione','複製の儀式',NULL,NULL,'Rito de replicación',NULL,'法术',NULL,'Rituel','Hexerei','Stregoneria','ソーサリー',NULL,NULL,'Conjuro',NULL,'增幅{5}（你可以在施放此咒语时额外支付{5}。）将一个衍生物放进战场，此衍生物为目标生物之复制品。如果模造仪式已增幅，则改为将五个此类衍生物放进战场。',NULL,'Kick {5} #_(Vous pouvez payer {5} supplémentaires au moment où vous lancez ce sort.)_# Mettez sur le champ de bataille un jeton qui est une copie de la créature ciblée. Si le Rite de duplication a été kické, mettez sur le champ de bataille cinq de ces jetons à la place.','Bonus {5} #_(Du kannst zusätzlich {5} bezahlen, sowie du diesen Zauberspruch wirkst.)_# Bringe einen Spielstein ins Spiel, der eine Kopie einer Kreatur deiner Wahl ist. Falls die Bonuskosten von Replikationsritual bezahlt wurden, bringe stattdessen fünf dieser Spielsteine ins Spiel.','Potenziamento {5} #_(Puoi pagare {5} addizionale mentre lanci questa magia.)_# Metti sul campo di battaglia una pedina che è una copia di una creatura bersaglio. Se il Rito di Riproduzione è stato potenziato, metti invece cinque di quelle pedine sul campo di battaglia.','キッカー{5}（あなたはこの呪文を唱えるに際し、追加で{5}を支払ってもよい。）クリーチャー１体を対象とし、それのコピーであるトークンを１体戦場に出す。複製の儀式がキッカーされていたなら、代わりにそのトークンを５体戦場に出す。',NULL,NULL,'Estímulo {5}. #_(Puedes pagar {5} adicionales al lanzar este hechizo.)_# Pon en el campo de batalla una ficha que es una copia de la criatura objetivo. Si el Rito de replicación fue estimulado, en vez de eso, pon en el campo de batalla cinco de esas fichas.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('405361','Rite of the Raging Storm','C15','Enchantment','U','{3}{R}{R}','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Creatures named Lightning Rager can''t attack you or planeswalkers you control.£At the beginning of each player''s upkeep, that player creates a 5/1 red Elemental creature token named Lightning Rager. It has trample, haste, and "At the beginning of the end step, sacrifice this creature."',NULL,NULL,'Svetlin Velinov','30','5','£11/4/2015: If Rite of the Raging Storm leaves the battlefield before attackers are declared, creatures named Lightning Rager can attack you or planeswalkers you control.£11/4/2015: The tokens aren’t named Elemental. They are named only Lightning Rager. The rule that says a token’s name is its creature types applies only if t